☁️ Deployment
Render (Backend + Pathway Worker)
Vercel (Frontend)
♻️ Waste Categories

The model classifies waste into:

Organic
Recyclable
Hazardous
Plastic
Metal
Glass

🔁 Real-Time Streaming Workflow
User uploads an image
Backend predicts waste type
Prediction is stored in waste_log.csv
Pathway continuously monitors the file
Real-time aggregation updates waste counts
Dashboard reflects live statistics
📦 Local Setup & Installation
1️⃣ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/green-ai.git
cd green-ai
2️⃣ Create Virtual Environment
python -m venv venv

Activate environment:

Linux / Mac
source venv/bin/activate
Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
3️⃣ Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
4️⃣ Run Backend Server
uvicorn backend.app:app --reload

👉 Open:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
5️⃣ Run Pathway Streaming
python pathway_pipeline/stream.py
🌍 Deployment Details
🚀 Backend + Pathway (Render)

Start Command:

uvicorn backend.app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 10000

Background Worker:

python pathway_pipeline/stream.py
🎨 Frontend (Vercel)
Simple HTML + JavaScript interface
Connected to FastAPI backend
Displays predictions and live stats
